1.10

950210	 452	Optimizimizing... The last 4 bytes required 8 hours of
		work!

950209	 468	Abandoned LeoClockLocation2, optimized code with the
		help of Pasi Ojala and Janne Salmijärvi.

1.01

930628	 488	Made an extra version, LeoClockLocation2, which opens
